quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"Ku izina ry’Imana, Nyirimpuhwe, Nyiramahane"
  1,2,"Ndakengurukiye Imana, Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  1,3,"Nyene Imigisha myinshi, na nyene Imigisha mito mito"
  1,4,Nyene inganji y’umusi w’imperuka
  1,5,"Niwewe dusenga, kandi niwewe dusaba imfashanyo"
  1,6,Turongore munzira igororotse
  1,7,"Inzira yabo wahaye imigisha kuribo, kandi atari mubashavuriwe kuribo, canke mubazimiye"
